{"tid":1934939,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行山撚] 衞奕信徑現炸彈 EOD即場引爆","createTime":"2020-03-20T08:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T08:58:17.000Z","uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81d7a1a4e8999f3c00c1f88c6b50cbbd83e10d39","tid":1934939,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>港島衞奕信徑現疑戰時手榴彈 EOD即場引爆</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本港不時發現戰時炸彈，今晨(20日)11時44分，警方接獲一名外籍人士報案，指在港島衞奕信徑1段行山時，在孖崗山一山坡處，發現5個懷疑手榴彈。消防員在赤柱硤道巴士站集合後，出發前往現場調查。<br />\n警方封鎖現場及附近一條行山徑，爆炸品處理課人員及後帶同工具到場處理，經過仔細檢視及判斷情況後，於下午約4時即場引爆。據悉，當中4枚手榴彈屬日本製，其餘1枚屬英國製，它們長約6吋，已經生銹，相信是戰時「遺物」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200320/photo/bkn-20200320132834174-0320_00822_001_02b.jpg?20200320164603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200320%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200320132834174-0320_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20200320164603&h=d9e8b952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200320/photo/bkn-20200320132834174-0320_00822_001_03b.jpg?20200320164603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200320%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200320132834174-0320_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20200320164603&h=58cddc75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed1d9f0a9d786a80e85e64606b7e5d9078424731","tid":1934939,"uid":116545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:52:07.000Z","msg":"黑警又會入年青人數嫁la🥱"},{"pid":"d4348010ea932915a11b9d1ba805120f3448ddfc","tid":1934939,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"見到炸彈就即場引爆 咁見到白粉咪...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd8aff1ed7e4b4b1ff3b4313fbc1f0459f961a6","tid":1934939,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:58: